column2: SELECT s.SpecObjID, s.z, s.fiberMag_r, s.sn_#, L.ew, L.sigma, L.sigmaErr, K.ew, K.sigma, K.sigmaErr FROM SpecObj as s, SpecLine as L, SpecLine as K WHERE    (L.LineID = #)    and (K.LineID = #)    and    and L.ew/nullif(L.ewErr,#)>#   and s.z IS NOT NULL   and s.sn_# > #   and s.objType = # ORDER BY s.mag_#
